metadata.name: flwr 01
metadata.description:
Mixture of textures present in the urban environment. The roughness of rust proof paint, the warmth of bricks, and the softness of plants all come together to create a visually dynamic and interesting space. My work aims to capture and highlight the beauty found in the contrasts of the city. The smoothness of glass and metal buildings in contrast with the roughness of a brick wall, the naturalness of a park amidst the man-made architecture.
